'''扎卡里·伊斯雷爾·「札克」·布瑞夫'''（{{lang-en|'''Zachary Israel " Zach " Braff'''}}，{{bd|1975年|4月6日}}）<ref name=tvgbio>{{cite web | url = http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/zach-braff/179781 | title = Zach Braff | publisher = [[TV_Guide|TVGuide.com]] | accessdate = April 29, 2014 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140401032643/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/zach-braff/179781 | archivedate = 2014年4月1日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員、喜劇演員、導演、編劇和製片人。他最著名的作品是在電視劇《[[實習醫生成長記|實習醫生成長記]]》中飾演Dr. John Dorian角色。

== 個人生平 ==
扎克·布拉夫在美國紐澤西州[[南奧蘭治|南奧蘭治]]出生並長大。他的父親Harold Irwin Braff是辯護律師和社會學教授，母親Anne Hutchinson是臨床心理學家<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/zach-braff-interview-scrubs-star-on-new-film-wish-i-was-here-and-pushing-40-9744274.html|title=Zach Braff interview: Scrubs star on 'pushing 40' and his new film|author=|date=2014-09-19|work=|newspaper=The Independent|accessdate=2018-05-19|language=|archive-date=2018-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519204802/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/zach-braff-interview-scrubs-star-on-new-film-wish-i-was-here-and-pushing-40-9744274.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，哥哥{{tsl|en|Joshua Braff|喬舒亞·布拉夫}}是作家<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/10168/|title=Another Braff Tale of Jewish Ennui|author=Naomi Pfefferman|last=|first=|date=2004-09-16|work=|newspaper=Jewish Journal|accessdate=2018-05-19|language=|archive-date=2018-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519205042/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/10168/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/1.5064371|title='Scrubs' Star Zach Braff Falls in Love With Tel Aviv|author=|last=Kupfer|first=Ruta|date=2008-11-24|work=|newspaper=Haaretz|accessdate=2018-05-19|language=|archive-date=2018-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180520053928/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/1.5064371|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thejc.com/culture/interviews/interview-zach-braff-1.31461|title=Interview: Zach Braff|accessdate=2018-05-19|author=Anne Joseph|date=February 2, 2012|work=The Jewish Chronicle|publisher=|archive-date=2018-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519205216/https://www.thejc.com/culture/interviews/interview-zach-braff-1.31461|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://njjewishnews.com/article/34317/hal-braff-honored-for-devotion-to-black-and-jewish-communities|title=Hal Braff honored for devotion to black and Jewish communities|accessdate=2018-05-19|author=Robert Wiener|date=May 18, 2017|work=New Jersey Jewish News - NJJN|publisher=}}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。母親有英格蘭、愛爾蘭和蘇格蘭血統<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0103785/bio|title=Zach Braff - Biography|accessdate=|author=|date=|work=IMDb|publisher=|quote=Zach's father is of Ashkenazi Jewish descent. Zach's mother is from a family of English, Irish, and Scottish ancestry.|archive-date=2018-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302082950/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0103785/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扎克·布拉夫曾經就讀希伯來學校，並且他接受了猶太教的成年禮（Bar Mitzvah）儀式<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jta.org/2018/03/27/arts-entertainment/zach-braff-happy-back-tv-scrubs-fans|title=Zach Braff is happy to be back on TV. ‘Scrubs’ fans should be, too.|accessdate=2018-05-19|author=Curt Schleier|date=March 27, 2018|work=JTA - Jewish news|publisher=|language=|quote=Braff attended Hebrew school and was a bar mitzvah at Oheb Shalom Congregation in South Orange.|archive-date=2018-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180520054100/https://www.jta.org/2018/03/27/arts-entertainment/zach-braff-happy-back-tv-scrubs-fans|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

